      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-athar-husain-rizvi-&-sayed-maqsood-athar": [
          "5. It was narrated to me by Muhammad b. Ali b. Majluwayh from Muhammad b. Abi al-Qasim from Ahmad b. Abi Abdillah from Mansur b. al-Abbas from Sa’eed b. Janah from Sulayman b. Ja’far al-Ja’fari from Abi al-Hassan (a.s.) who said: “Black dye is the cause of beauty for women and a cause of defeat of enemies.”"
        ]
